                <h1 class="article-main-title">The Athens Affair</h1>

                <h2 class="article-dek">How some extremely smart hackers pulled off the most audacious cell-network break-in ever</h2>

                
                    <div class="auth-byline">
                        By <span class="author-name">Vassilis Prevelakis and Diomidis Spinellis</span>
                    </div>
                
                


